parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the smart glass switch can cause the windows to roll up and down independently, draining the battery and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The windows roll up and down on their own
even when the car is turned off and the key is not in the vehicle
draining the battery
and causing the vehicle to not start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the battery to drain, the vehicle to not start, and potentially lead to a fire.
symptoms: The battery drains
the vehicle does not start
smoke or fire comes from the cigarette lighter
and the electrical system overheats.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door module can cause the windows to malfunction, drain the battery, and potentially leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The windows do not roll down when opening the door
the windows roll up and down on their own
and the battery drains.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment or incorrect deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in an accident
the passenger airbag light illuminates intermittently
the side curtain airbags and driver's seat airbag deploy erroneously.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the non-deployment or incorrect deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the radio volume increases when the steering wheel is turned.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TAKATA airbag inflators can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the non-deployment or incorrect deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag light illuminates intermittently
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the battery is dead
the dashboard lights come on
and the power steering and brakes are lost.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to be difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering is hard to turn
the steering wheel is stiff
and there is a whining or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard lights come on
the vehicle stalls
and the power steering and brakes are lost.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of suspension and steering components can cause the vehicle to be difficult to control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
there is a snapping or clicking noise
and the steering is difficult to control.
